data.description: Welcome HOME! This pristine turnkey home in the Walnut Grove subdivision offers four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms. It features an open-concept living area with a gourmet kitchen, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining, boasting granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The luxurious master suite includes a spa-like ensuite bathroom. Outside, a beautifully landscaped yard provides a perfect space for outdoor relaxation. Conveniently located, this home combines luxury, comfort, and convenience for an unparalleled living experience.
